   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">N/A
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">xt = x + dcos(direction);
yt = y - dsin(direction);
zt = z - dsin(zdirection);
audio_listener_position(x, y, z)
audio_listener_orientation(xt, yt, zt, 0, 0, 1)
</code></pre>
